name: Cushion insert - Fibre    40 x 60 cm
description:
Fibre cushion insert to fit our 40x60cm rectangular cushion covers.
The recycled PET fibre is derived from post consumer water bottles. 
The fibre looks, feels and performs in the same way as a high grade poly fibre, but is completely recycled.
For every 1 kg of fibre used, we save around 70 plastic water bottles from ending up in landfills.
Hand wash and line dry.
This fibre is non-allergenic and antibacterial.
Made in Australia
